text: Central Airport is a 1933 American adventure drama movie directed by William A. Wellman and Alfred E. Green. It stars Richard Barthelmess, Sally Eilers, Tom Brown, Grant Mitchell, Claire McDowell, John Wayne and was distributed by Warner Bros. ==References== ==Other websites== * * * Category:1933 drama movies Category:1930s American adventure movies Category:1930s American drama movies Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by Alfred E.
